{
  "stem": "17299.6",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "From the cat [LAUGHS] for the other fellow.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Some were fair.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Some were very anti-Semitic.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the camp commander was a bastard.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "His name was [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there was one ethnic German from Romania.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "His name was [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He did a lot of beating.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He knocked my tooth out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I run out of the kitchen.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I had diarrhea.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I bumped into him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He caught me begging.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he hit me with a pistol butt in the mouth, and it broke a tooth.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "With the civilian, we had no contact.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Keep the Jews on working.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There is a factory going.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When the front came closer, the next action was to take us away.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it was decided to take us to Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I would say, yes, because there were over 1,500 prisoners left in the camp.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They had sent out a couple of thousand, which were sick, prior to that to Bergen-Belsen.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And from those who were sent to Bergen-Belsen, there is no survivor.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because I tried to trace them after the war, and there is no survive.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were put in boxcars, 50 to a boxcar.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we were sent via Dresden into the [NON-ENGLISH] Mountain.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We came to a stop.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was called [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we had to dig a grave for those who had died already.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And-- [? while we ?] after we had buried those, we got back in the train.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They gave us some food.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then the train moved out with two engines.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then we were maybe a few miles away, the train got attacked by American fighter planes.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
